body_answer:
If you use PBKDF2WithHmacSHA1 instead of PBEWithSHA1andDESede your assumption works as it supports salt. You just need to add a the keyLength parameter to PBEKeySpec:
        String algo = "PBKDF2WithHmacSHA1";

