db.store(hashedText);

body_answer:
In both your methods the salt is predictable, so only one rainbow table is needed.
You should use a different salt every time you hash a string:
plainText = input();
salt = getRandomSalt();
hashedText = hash(salt + plainText);
db.store(salt, hashedText);

